author-11a_esS_09VNjvlkNmasVQ">Vũ Lãm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trinh-Khanh/T%E1%BA%A1i-V%C5%A9-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A1c/poem-txYgLzrSj4evlbAfmwVpfA">Tại Vũ Xương tác - 在武昌作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trinh-Khanh/author-Ilze63P8CwiNVC4ocnEpgg">Từ Trinh Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-%C4%90%C4%83ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Qu%C3%BD-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ho%C3%A0n-kinh/poem-3aDWftFHvcbz_LQZncZLRA">Tống Nhạc Quý Phương hoàn kinh - 送岳季方還京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-%C4%90%C4%83ng/author-f0pHwz1tzFQ4ho5N8P_VfQ">Quách Đăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/T%C6%B0-quy/poem-wr4YllSw1u6I5OZE8rW7zg">Tư quy - 思歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/author-sRwDvUqTTXJgu1Qk5ewg6w">Vi Trang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-L%C3%A3ng/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BB%ADu-th%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-5pzTdsGdV1rfu2PyNjnJyA">Xuân nhật đối tửu thư sự - 春日對酒書事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-L%C3%A3ng/author-QcVcrL73Uo9raEQzmrL0vA">Phan Lãng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
